            <p>Worth It Studio is committed to ensuring that our website is accessible to all people, including people with disabilities.</p>
            <p>We strive to make our website accessible in accordance with the Israeli Equal Rights for Persons with Disabilities Regulations and the WCAG 2.1 Level AA guidelines.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content-block">
            <h2 class="text-start">Accessibility features on this website</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>The website is built with semantic HTML for easy navigation.</li>
                <li>Images include alternative text (alt) descriptions.</li>
                <li>The website supports keyboard navigation.</li>
                <li>The website is compatible with screen readers.</li>
                <li>The website is responsive and adapts to different screen sizes and devices.</li>
            </ul>
